body.description: G.I. Joe is a highly skilled, on-demand, special operations force of men and women from around the globe. These extraordinarily talented heroes are selected for their elite abilities and tasked with defending the world from Cobra, a ruthless criminal organization bent on total domination. With unwavering courage and steely determination, the brave members of G.I. Joe are prepared to seek out Cobra in any environment on the planet. From hostile jungles to ice-clad arctic peaks…wherever there’s trouble, G.I. Joe is there. These Croc Master & Fiona figures come ready for action, with multiple points of articulation for high poseability and 7 character-inspired accessories. And with custom artwork by Luke Preece, the G.I. Joe Classified Series Croc Master & Fiona package will make a mark on shelves.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing figures, especially the croc
reviews.reviewText: These are fantastic. Was not expecting to love Croc Master, as he's kind of goofy, but the figure itself is great, amazing texturing on his outfit and the same great articulation of other Classified figures. Fun accessories, too.The standout though, is the fully articulated crocodile. Extremely detailed and posable. Amazing figure, and would love to see more animals in this line.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 23, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars You'll Love This Set But You'd Better Get That Hairdryer
reviews.reviewText: I love this figure but boy oh boy are Crocmaster's hand and Fiona's joints tight! I needed the hairdryer to soften up a lot of plastic. The sculptwork on both figures is amazing, and the paintwork is top-notch too. Crocmaster comes with a lot of accessories: 2 baby crocodiles, a permanently coiled whip, a hook, his revolver and knife, and Fiona's collar and leash. The collar is permanently attached to the leash, and the leash does have a little flexibility but don't expect anything crazy from it. The collar is extremely tight, and had to be heated up in order to slide over Fiona's head. The knife sheath was also insanely tight, and a flexible plastic knife just wasn't going in there without the hairdryer treatment. Crocmaster's hands weren't opening up for any accessories without that hairdryer either. The baby crocodiles are adorable as heck, and add a bit of cuteness to the set.Fiona has a flexible tail that you can bend just a little bit. The tail's ball socket joint at the base does most of the work. The legs have joints at the base of the body and the feet have forward joints and ankle rockers. The foot joints are super-tight, and once again I had to call on that hairdryer to break them loose. She has a diaphram-like segment that allows for decent forward legs and head movement.I'm really happy with this figure. I had initially planned to pass on it because I don't remember Crocmaster being in the original tv show, but I'm glad I finally decided to buy. Just make sure you use hot water or a hairdryer to help with a lot of tight plastic going on with this set.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars slightly over priced
reviews.reviewText: This is the g.i. joe classified deluxe croc master figure number 38 in the line. Figure comes with one over size croc a few baby crocs a whip chain, hook and a pistol. Figure is a good representation of the character. The giant crock is full articulated. My issues was there were not enough items to warrant a deluxe price. I feel they could have included the a few more weapons like his rifle and giant manchette that the venom vs valor version of this figure had . I do recommend picking this up but wait till it is on sale as they are want too much for a figure that does not come with enough accessory's to warrant a deluxe price.
